4\\uc9c0 \\uc81c\\uc791, \\ubbff\\uace0 \\ub9e1\\uae38 \\uc218 \\uc788\\ub294 \\uc5c5\\uccb4\\ub97c \\ucc3e\\uace0 \\uacc4\\uc2e0\\uac00\\uc694? \\uc624\\ub79c \\uc81c\\uc791 \\uacbd\\ud5d8\\uacfc \\ud0c4\\ud0c4\\ud55c \\ub178\\ud558\\uc6b0\\ub97c \\uac16\\ucd98 <strong>THEVOS<\\/strong>\\ub97c \\ucd94\\ucc9c\\ub4dc\\ub9bd\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. \\uace0\\uac1d\\uc774 \\ub9cc\\uc871\\ud558\\ub294 \\ud648\\ud398\\uc774\\uc9c0\\ub97c \\ud568\\uaed8 \\ub9cc\\ub4e4\\uc5b4 \\ub4dc\\ub9ac\\uaca0\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<\\/p>\\n      <p class=\\\"cta-sub\\\">\\ubbf8\\uc6a9\\uc2e4 \\ud648\\ud398\\uc774\\uc9c0 \\uc81c\\uc791\\uc5d0 \\uad00\\ud574 \\uad81\\uae08\\ud55c \\uc810\\uc774 \\uc788\\uc73c\\uc2dc\\ub2e4\\uba74 \\uc5b8\\uc81c\\ub4e0\\uc9c0 \\ud3b8\\ud558\\uac8c \\ubb38\\uc758\\ud574\\uc8fc\\uc138\\uc694.<\\/p>\\n    <\\/div>\\n  <\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div class=\\\"page\\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\\"hero\\\">\\n\\t\\t<p class=\\\"hero-eyebrow\\\">Hair Salon Website Guide<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t<h1 class=\\\"hero-title\\\">Are you thinking about creating a website for your hair salon?<\\/h1>\\n\\t\\t<p class=\\\"hero-desc\\\">Here\'s what to prepare before contacting a web design agency \\u2014 having this information ready will make consultations smoother and speed up the entire production process.<\\/p>\\n\\t<\\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\\"steps\\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step-num\\\">1<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-title\\\">Gather your salon\'s basic information<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-desc\\\">Make sure you have your salon name, address, phone number, email, and business hours ready to share.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step-num\\\">2<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-title\\\">Take photos of your salon interior and exterior<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-desc\\\">If possible, also capture photos of the services you provide. Photos are a powerful way to communicate your salon\'s atmosphere and the quality of your work.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step\\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step-num\\\">3<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-title\\\">List your services and pricing<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-desc\\\">Organize the types of hair services you offer along with their prices, and write a brief description for each. This helps potential customers understand what\'s available and what to expect in terms of cost.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step-num\\\">4<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-title\\\">Collect reviews from past customers<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-desc\\\">Customer reviews help establish trust and demonstrate the quality of your services to new visitors.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"step-num\\\">5<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-title\\\">Highlight what makes your salon special<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\\"step-desc\\\">Summarize any unique services, experiences, or expertise your salon offers. This is your chance to showcase what sets you apart from the competition.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t<\\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\\"cta-card\\\">\\n\\t\\t<p class=\\\"cta-label\\\">Contact Us<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t<p class=\\\"cta-text\\\">Looking for a reliable web design agency to build your hair salon website? We recommend <strong>Us (Earth)<\\/strong> \\u2014 with years of experience and proven expertise, we\'re here to help you create a website you\'ll be proud of.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t<p class=\\\"cta-sub\\\">If you have any questions about hair salon website development, feel free to reach out anytime.<\\/p>\\n\\t<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\",\"ja\":\"<div class=\\\"page\\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\\"hero\\\">\